In a first aspect, therefore, the present invention relates to a composition which comprises the following myelin basic protein peptides:



    

MBP 30-44;

MBP 83-99;

MBP 131-145; and

MBP 140-154.

In a third aspect, the present invention provides a kit which comprises the following myelin basic protein peptides:



    

MBP 30-44;

MBP 83-99;

MBP 131-145; and

MBP 140-154


for simultaneous, separate or sequential administration.
